Package: usa.gov
Title: U.S. Government Executive Orders and Website Analytics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for usa.gov data.
    Wraps the Federal Register executive orders API and analytics.usa.gov
    real-time website analytics. Includes LLM context injection via usag_context().
